{"tid":1958362,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過右邊上腹肋骨位痛","createTime":"2020-04-04T14:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T14:59:14.000Z","uid":8114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"14fd7dd69feb81db5391f74dc1a6500fad6f897b","tid":1958362,"uid":8114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T14:51:39.000Z","msg":"前幾日訓醒無啦啦右上腹肋骨個位按壓痛，坐同企都唔痛，係用手按落去先痛，去醫院驗完血＆尿，照完超聲波＆X光，醫生都係話肝膽無事都正常，check唔到啲咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家都成日都會禁下個位，禁完痛又亂諗，想問下有無人試過上腹最下邊條肋骨位痛嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c364b67a17fd05ef94878cfadb2c1b80c0f8b060","tid":1958362,"uid":92453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"試過右下又係禁佢先痛，或者伸懶腰就痛<br />\n又係照肺，照超聲波無野<br />\n<br />\n之後唔理佢就無咩事"},{"pid":"263c829fb0bbb1a79d9f51f32444cdd9a58db22c","tid":1958362,"uid":52638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T14:53:47.000Z","msg":"似係橫隔膜問題？<br />\n呼吸嗰啲有冇事先"},{"pid":"dae0f13a6f6a691bbba403ba2b9e76cdf93ca01c","tid":1958362,"uid":8114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c364b67a17fd05ef94878cfadb2c1b80c0f8b060","tid":1958362,"uid":92453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"試過右下又係禁佢先痛，或者伸懶腰就痛<br />\n又係照肺，照超聲波無野<br />\n<br />\n之後唔理佢就無咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"係啊，側訓都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbbbfcbe3e31395d10cfa7949187fac1ccab7ba","tid":1958362,"uid":8114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"263c829fb0bbb1a79d9f51f32444cdd9a58db22c","tid":1958362,"uid":52638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T14:53:47.000Z","msg":"似係橫隔膜問題？<br />\n呼吸嗰啲有冇事先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"呼吸無野，係按到同個腹用力整到就痛"}]}